title: Dane asks: What if everyone had a superpower? (Whomanji Part 2)
description:
The Jammaloo Family faces level two of the Whomanji game. Will they get their power-ups and finally have an awesome training montage?

Lessons include: even grownups (and older siblings) sometimes need to be reminded of their own lessons; practicing together is a lot more productive than showing off alone.
